---
title: Nan's Chargrilled Sirloin Steak & Avocado-Rocket Salad with Creamy Mustard Potatoes
description: Nothing beats a good chargrilled steak. Paired with a peppery avocado-rocket salad and mustardy potatoes, it's a winning barbeque meal. No barbie? No worries. Just follow our tips for cooking on the stove or in the oven!
